line_1: Thou veriest Fool (she cry'd) of all my Brats;
line_2: Thou base, degen'rate Seed of injur'd Rats,

line_1: Thou veriest Fool (she cry'd) of all my Brats;
line_2: Woud'st thou have shaken Hands with hostile Cats,

line_1: Each fortnight once she bears to see the brats,
line_2: "For oh they stun one's ears, like squalling cats!"
